{"tid":1275770,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"自助繪療區","createTime":"2019-07-01T22:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T15:29:17.000Z","uid":240962,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a7eb42bd40adc85fcede6b53d04ad311c82379d7","tid":1275770,"uid":240962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:59:48.000Z","msg":"防止自殺潮！！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n 有見大家因時勢而精神壓力巨大，情況嚴峻。我知道大家都好無力，唔知道有咩可以幫到大家，於是想臨時開設藝療區，不設專員導引，純粹自己響畫紙上亂鳩咁畫下。當私人藝術周記咁，釋放壓力，舒緩身心。<br />\n不需要交流，如想傾計，亦可跟在場畫友傾計。不需要有畫技，只需要放慢自己，放下繃緊的神經。<br />\n現場播下d輕鬆音樂。<br />\n<br />\n唔諗住賺，唔諗住交租俾業主(喂)，只收返少少物資費，蝕本就蝕本。<br />\n＄40元/1人(一個半小時至兩小時)<br />\n&uarr;多人報既話睇下可唔可能再減價，我知好多學生憤戰左咁耐已經無咩錢😣有困難但好需要黎休養精神畫下畫的話就私聊同我講啦💆但希望大家唔好濫用私聊減費😖等更有需要既人得到幫助👩&zwj;❤️&zwj;💋&zwj;👩<br />\n<br />\n日期：見表格內，隨時更新<br />\n<br />\n詳情請加tg群之後再細閱。<br />\n<br />\n報名請填一填表格：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScVi3Tit39tCHbJj1GpWx8CrsdhTWhBj4Fo6wNCsCH1x35Oew/viewform?usp=pp_url\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScVi3Tit39tCHbJj1GpWx8CrsdhTWhBj4Fo6wNCsCH1x35Oew%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dpp_url&d=9Ou39NWu4C7Ce3sh0Mn9C5B82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=d40e492a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScVi3Tit39tCHbJj1GpWx8CrsdhTWhBj4Fo6wNCsCH1x35Oew/viewform?usp=pp_url</a>"},{"pid":"93d8d27ad7472740db61bcc7514d83b3db63d208","tid":1275770,"uid":73855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T23:01:48.000Z","msg":"[文宣-7.1衝立會] 給父母的信<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1275224\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1275224</a>"},{"pid":"97be9f55ae7db8b0d65a60425531450a15e108b1","tid":1275770,"uid":240962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:00:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a795928671dbd6f2ec2c06e3e76e5c9714d7cf69","tid":1275770,"uid":240962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0